{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Es eſmu gauscht apfirdſis\nun fohtt fadaufhts/ es kanzu\nmannas Sir̈ds Kuhſſchanas\ndeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. KlINGS preekſch tewim\nirr wiffa manna Eekahroſchana/\nun mannas Nopuhſchanas ne\nirr preekſch tewim apflehptas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Manua Sir̈ds trihz/\nmans Spehks irr manna atſtah-\njis/ ir patti mannu Azzu Gaif-\nmina pee mannim newaid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Mannt Mihte un man-\nni Draugi ſtahw iſtahtam no\nmannas Mohzibas/ un manni\nTuwaſi ſtahw no tahtenes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un kas mannu Dwehteli\nmekle/ leek man Walqis/ un kas\nmannu Launu mekle/ runna no\nRaifehn/ un iſdohma Wiltibu\nzaurn Deenu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Bet es eſmu ta patt ka\nkuris/kas ne dſird/ un ka mehms/\nkas jawu Mutti ne atweer.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Un es eſmu ka weens dutuna.\nWihrs/ kas ne dſird/ un kurra\nMutte Aisbildinaſchanas ne-\nwaid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Jo es gaidu KlINGS\nus tewi/tu paklaufiſi/KlINGS\nmans Deews.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "17. Jo es fazzihu : Lai tee\npahr mannim ne vreezajahs/ kad\nmannu Rahja fchaubitohs/ tad\ntee buhtu prett maũ leelijufchees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "18. Jo es eſmu tai Kriſcha-\nnai tuwu/ un mannas Sahpes\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Jo mannu Noseegu-\nes iſſuhdsu/ un man irr\nmannu Grehku deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Bet manni Eenaide-\ndſihwo/ un irr warreni/ un\nmann par nepateeft eenihd/ w\nrojahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Un kas Launu par Lab-\nmaſta/ tee ſtahw prett man-\ntapehz ka es us to Labbu-\ndſennohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Ne atſtabjees no manni-\nKlINGS mans Deews! ne e-\ntahtu no mannim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Steidſees man par Ba-\ngu/ Kungs/ manna Beſtifchan\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "irr weenumehr preekſch manni-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXXIX. Dseesma.\nIrr weena luhdsama Dseesma/ eeſich fa Do-\nwids luhds/ ka Deews wiſchu ne liktu ne-\nzeettgu tapt pahr teem Beſdeewigem/ t-\ntik drohſchi un lainigi dſihwo : 1. Q-\nwifſwairak mahziht apdohmaht/ fahda\nfa fchi Dſihwiba efju: 6. Jo wiſch-\nrejus us Deewu: 8. etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "1. �Eena Dahwida Dsee-\nina/ preekſch ta augi-\nDseedataja preekſch I-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Es eſmu apnehunces/ ka e-\nfawn Zeltu gribbu paſargah-\nta es ne grehkoju ar fawn Me-\nli/ es ſargafchu fawn Mutti t-\npatt ka ar Eemauteem/ kamel-\ntas Beſdeewigs prett manu ir-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. Es eſmu ka mehms paliz-\nzis/ un kluſſu zeetis/ un ne pe-\ninnu to Labbu/ bet manna-\nSahpes tvatrojahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Manua Sir̈ds irr eekah-\nsusi eeſich mannim/ kad es us t-\ndo-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
